Honestly the food is good. Very tasty, made with love! The amount of takeout orders tells me that the locals appreciate this place too! I only did takeout but the young lady behind the counter was very polite.

The atmosphere could be better. The AC was out, making it unfortunately difficult to hangout there. Their once beautiful ceiling is now falling apart. It needed to be fixed. It‚Äôs hard to feel comfortable dining in. Looks to me like it used to be a really cozy spot, back in the day. If they ever bring it back to life, I‚Äôll come back and spend time there!
The worst breakfast ƒ± have ever had. Hashbrowns were disgusting and they cant read or they don‚Äôt have any idea about how to make an omelette.

This place is amazing... You all should go here... I customized my own food.. my uncle got the corned beef and hash.. He asked for it burnt. Waffle fries are amazing. I got the skillet customized with chicken tenders, tots/waffle fries.. Sour cream, rice, beans, topped with melted cheddar cheese... And the iced coffee mocha w/almond milk is also great.. Jasmine is so good at making iced coffee. Shardi is there on Sundays and so friendly...Brian is the best chef.. And the owner Mark is such a nice and welcoming guy! Come here whenever you can! Never a disappointment.

Fantastic gyros. 8$ for a lamb gyro is a steal. It was a little bit run down but I can‚Äôt blame them, it seemed like 2 people working hard to keep a restaurant going. 5/5 stars, would definitely go again

This place is as good as it gets! To start, they serve the best coffee I have ever had. I tried a few different dishes and everything was truly delicious. From the first bite to the last, I can honestly say I loved absolutely everything I tried.

Even though it was my first visit, the owner personally introduced himself and made me feel welcomed. The staff member that helped me was willing to answer all my questions and she was a real pleasure to talk with. The hospitality here is top tier.

I can't recommend this restaurant enough, this experience has definitely made me become a regular costumer as I will be back soon!
